# Quick Start

### 1. Initialize the library
```javascript
await HRN.init();
```

### 2. Get the current list
```javascript
console.log(HRN.list);
```

### 3. Get one random game
```javascript
const game = HRN.random().list[0];
console.log(game.name);
```

### 4. Get one random game (new shortcut)
```javascript
const game = HRN.getRandomOne();
console.log(game.name);
```
